stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Disconnected
    Disconnected --> Connecting : Page loads
    Connecting --> Connected : WebSocket open
    Connecting --> Failed : Connection error
    Failed --> Connecting : Retry
    Connected --> MessageReceived : Alert arrives
    MessageReceived --> Connected : Process & display
    Connected --> Disconnected : Page closes
    Connected --> Reconnecting : Connection lost
    Reconnecting --> Connected : Reconnected